summary: AN ORDINANCE relating to Plat 39E, Page 24-339 of the Seattle Municipal code (page 109 of the Official Zoning Map of The City of Seattle, Ordinance 86300), accepting an amendment to the Property Use and Development Agreement which was accepted by Ordinance 103666 and filled in C.F. 274605 in connection with the rezone of Blocks 182 and 187, Seattle Tidelands, from Manufacturing (M) Zone to Metropolitan Commercial (CM) Zone (Petition of Cornerstone Development Company; C.F. 289948).
